exports[`info > info Button --detail --format markdown 1`] = `
"Button (жҢүй’®) вҖ” To trigger an operation.

When to use: A button means an operation (or a series of operations). Clicking a button will trigger its corresponding business logic.

In Ant Design we provide 5 types of button.

- рҹ”ө Primary button: used for the main action, there can be at most one primary button in a section.
- вҡӘпёҸ Default button: used for a series of actions without priority.
- рҹ«Ҙ Dashed button: commonly used for adding more actions.
- рҹ”Ө Text button: used for the most secondary action.
- рҹ”— Link button: used for external links.

And 4 other properties additionally.

- рҹ”ҙ \`danger\`: used for actions of risk, like deletion or authorization.
- рҹ‘» \`ghost\`: used in situations with complex background, home pages usually.
- рҹҡ« \`disabled\`: used when actions are not available.
- рҹ”ғ \`loading\`: adds a loading spinner in button, avoids multiple submits too.

| Property | Type | Default | Since | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| autoInsertSpace | boolean | \`true\` | 5.17.0 | We add a space between two Chinese characters by default, which removed by setting \`autoInsertSpace\` to \`false\`. |
| block | boolean | false | - | Option to fit button width to its parent width |
| classNames | [Record<SemanticDOM, string>](#semantic-dom) | - | 5.4.0 | Semantic DOM class |
| color | \`default\` \\| \`primary\` \\| \`danger\` \\| [PresetColors](#presetcolors) | - | \`default\`, \`primary\` and \`danger\`: 5.21.0, \`PresetColors\`: 5.23.0 | Set button color |
| danger | boolean | false | - | Syntactic sugar. Set the danger status of button. will follow \`color\` if provided |
| disabled | boolean | false | - | Disabled state of button |
| ghost | boolean | false | - | Make background transparent and invert text and border colors |
| href | string | - | - | Redirect url of link button |
| htmlType | \`submit\` \\| \`reset\` \\| \`button\` | \`button\` | \`button\` | Set the original html \`type\` of \`button\`, see: [MDN](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button#type) |
| icon | ReactNode | - | - | Set the icon component of button |
| iconPosition | \`start\` \\| \`end\` | \`start\` | 5.17.0 | Set the icon position of button |
| loading | boolean \\| { delay: number, icon: ReactNode } | false | 5.23.0 | Set the loading status of button |
| shape | \`default\` \\| \`circle\` \\| \`round\` | \`default\` | \`round\` | Can be used to set button shape |
| size | \`large\` \\| \`middle\` \\| \`small\` | \`middle\` | \`small\` | Set the size of button |
| styles | [Record<SemanticDOM, CSSProperties>](#semantic-dom) | - | 5.4.0 | Semantic DOM style |
| target | string | - | - | Same as target attribute of a, works when href is specified |
| type | \`primary\` \\| \`dashed\` \\| \`link\` \\| \`text\` \\| \`default\` | \`default\` | \`link\` \\ | Syntactic sugar. Set button type. Will follow \`variant\` & \`color\` if provided |
| onClick | (event: React.MouseEvent<HTMLElement, MouseEvent>) => void | - | - | Set the handler to handle \`click\` event |
| variant | \`outlined\` \\| \`dashed\` \\| \`solid\` \\| \`filled\` \\| \`text\` \\| \`link\` | - | 5.21.0 | Set button variant |"
`;

exports[`info > info Button --detail --format text 1`] = `
"Button (жҢүй’®) вҖ” To trigger an operation.

When to use: A button means an operation (or a series of operations). Clicking a button will trigger its corresponding business logic.

In Ant Design we provide 5 types of button.

- рҹ”ө Primary button: used for the main action, there can be at most one primary button in a section.
- вҡӘпёҸ Default button: used for a series of actions without priority.
- рҹ«Ҙ Dashed button: commonly used for adding more actions.
- рҹ”Ө Text button: used for the most secondary action.
- рҹ”— Link button: used for external links.

And 4 other properties additionally.

- рҹ”ҙ \`danger\`: used for actions of risk, like deletion or authorization.
- рҹ‘» \`ghost\`: used in situations with complex background, home pages usually.
- рҹҡ« \`disabled\`: used when actions are not available.
- рҹ”ғ \`loading\`: adds a loading spinner in button, avoids multiple submits too.

Property         Type                                                              Default    Since                                                              Description                                                                                                                
---------------  ----------------------------------------------------------------  ---------  -----------------------------------------------------------------  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
autoInsertSpace  boolean                                                           \`true\`     5.17.0                                                             We add a space between two Chinese characters by default, which removed by setting \`autoInsertSpace\` to \`false\`.           
block            boolean                                                           false      -                                                                  Option to fit button width to its parent width                                                                             
classNames       [Record<SemanticDOM, string>](#semantic-dom)                      -          5.4.0                                                              Semantic DOM class                                                                                                         
color            \`default\` | \`primary\` | \`danger\` | [PresetColors](#presetcolors)  -          \`default\`, \`primary\` and \`danger\`: 5.21.0, \`PresetColors\`: 5.23.0  Set button color                                                                                                           
danger           boolean                                                           false      -                                                                  Syntactic sugar. Set the danger status of button. will follow \`color\` if provided                                          
disabled         boolean                                                           false      -                                                                  Disabled state of button                                                                                                   
ghost            boolean                                                           false      -                                                                  Make background transparent and invert text and border colors                                                              
href             string                                                            -          -                                                                  Redirect url of link button                                                                                                
htmlType         \`submit\` | \`reset\` | \`button\`                                     \`button\`   \`button\`                                                           Set the original html \`type\` of \`button\`, see: [MDN](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button#type)
icon             ReactNode                                                         -          -                                                                  Set the icon component of button                                                                                           
iconPosition     \`start\` | \`end\`                                                   \`start\`    5.17.0                                                             Set the icon position of button                                                                                            
loading          boolean | { delay: number, icon: ReactNode }                      false      5.23.0                                                             Set the loading status of button                                                                                           
shape            \`default\` | \`circle\` | \`round\`                                    \`default\`  \`round\`                                                            Can be used to set button shape                                                                                            
size             \`large\` | \`middle\` | \`small\`                                      \`middle\`   \`small\`                                                            Set the size of button                                                                                                     
styles           [Record<SemanticDOM, CSSProperties>](#semantic-dom)               -          5.4.0                                                              Semantic DOM style                                                                                                         
target           string                                                            -          -                                                                  Same as target attribute of a, works when href is specified                                                                
type             \`primary\` | \`dashed\` | \`link\` | \`text\` | \`default\`                \`default\`  \`link\` \\                                                           Syntactic sugar. Set button type. Will follow \`variant\` & \`color\` if provided                                              
onClick          (event: React.MouseEvent<HTMLElement, MouseEvent>) => void        -          -                                                                  Set the handler to handle \`click\` event                                                                                    
variant          \`outlined\` | \`dashed\` | \`solid\` | \`filled\` | \`text\` | \`link\`      -          5.21.0                                                             Set button variant"
`;

